The final point in the Miss America crown is Success. To me, success is possible in every situation even if you "fail," as long as we learn, because learning allows growth. Several very famous and influential people "failed" by the world's standards, yet went on to find much success. For example, Oprah was fired from her dream job as a news anchor because she "wasn't fit for the job." Imagine if Oprah had not taken the opportunity to learn and grow and gave up on achieving her dreams. 
With that, I encourage each of you to define your success as learning from your "failures" and to believe in yourself and your ability to achieve your dreams. 
#success #MissNebraska2017 #growthmindset #MissAmerica #crown #believe #achieve
